description: SPO Networks, Inc. focuses on solid waste, scrap metal recycling, and demolition services. The company operates two scrap metal operations in Arkansas and Missouri to provide scrap metal to the steel industry and produces generic cannabis seeds for wholesale and retail customers Colorado. The company was formerly known as Highline Technical Innovations, Inc. and changed its name to SPO Networks, Inc. in 2016. SPO Networks, Inc. is based in Farmington, Arkansas.
